data.title: New Castle County Contact Information
data.meta_description: Contact information for the Delaware Court of Chancery in New Castle County Delaware.
data.text:
Court of Chancery

New Castle County

Leonard L. Williams Justice Center

500 North King Street

Wilmington, DE 19801

Hours: 8:30 am - 4:30 pm

Litigants with after hours or holiday emergency filings for Guardianships ONLY that need immediate Court attention should contact the Court by email at Chancery_Guardianship_Emergency_Filings@delaware.gov. Someone will be in contact with you.

Please do not use this email for communication to the Court regarding Civil Action cases. This is strictly for Guardianship Emergencies.
